1060
02:42:22,730 --> 02:42:25,480
擁有同一張臉孔嗎？
The features of the same face?

1061
02:42:40,290 --> 02:42:42,460
我的靈魂
Oh, my soul,

1062
02:42:44,080 --> 02:42:46,170
